  "description": "<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201305/c28f6ed441d84c13acf7cc6a9db85cd1.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t还在羡慕BBC播音员员一口地道标准的英式发音吗？想要练就纯正英音，《BBC英音模仿秀》帮你忙！《BBC英音模仿秀》是一档沪江部落的原创口语互动节目，主持人对音频进行重点讲解和示范模仿，并对大家递交的口语模仿作品进行一对一的点评！<a href=\"http://pass.hujiang.com/signup/?source=en_sqyd&amp;url=http://bulo.hujiang.com/menu/2120/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201305/7e2a59a999f44c92a141bbeff7458379.jpg\" /></a>去沪江部落订阅本节目！</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>今日主持人：xhlwrb</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>22秒音频： </strong><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p570695\" title=\"点击获得更好的阅读体验\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_video.gif\" /></a></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>主持人模仿音频： </strong><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p570695\" title=\"点击获得更好的阅读体验\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_video.gif\" /></a></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>模仿文本：</strong></p>\n<div class=\"langs_en\">\n\t<div class=\"langs_en\">\n\t\tThe games <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/industry\" target=\"_blank\">industry</a> hasn't woken up to the new consumer which is women who are driving the growth in industry. The big companies like Xbox and PlayStation don't put budget into <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/female\" target=\"_blank\">female</a> titles. They also are not actively recruiting women. We need more women involved in the design process. Currently, only 4% of all developers in the UK are female.游戏产业还没有意识到女性作为新兴消费者正在推动该产业的增长。一些大公司比如Xbox和PlayStation都没有针对女性职位的预算。他们也不主动招聘女性。我们需要更多女性参与游戏的设计过程。目前，英国仅有4%的游戏开发者是女性。</div>\n</div>\n<p>\n\t<strong>语调示意图：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://i1.s.hjfile.cn/entry/201312/d62ac4e5-41f8-4282-b8f6-0d886c975e77.jpg\" /></strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>重点单词发音讲解：</strong><span style=\"display: none;\">&nbsp;</span><br />\n\tfemale<br />\n\tindustry</p>\n<p>\n\t想要得到主持人专业的点评和意见吗？<a href=\"http://bulo.hujiang.com/menu/2120/